{
  "stem": "142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were the-- mostly in a-- a lot of a-- I remember a lot of sardines in cans, a lot of canned foods.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, some cakes, and this-- these type of things, that the people who are leaving the house, you know, they thought that they'll come, and they need some provisions for a few days, or--",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they're-- you know, they get flabbergasted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not many times we had the opportunity either, you know, to-- to tell them, you know, We were around there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, SS were around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they get undressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And right away, they were going direct to the chambers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since it takes a few minutes to die, you know, then they realized that they were dying, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you always, you'll find, when you open the doors, a lot of scratches in the walls of blood.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, with-- they're going with their fingers, you know, scratching the walls, to be able to get-- get saved someplace.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no way out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What language would you speak to these people?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How would you communicate?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, it depends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we were talking-- we were taking French, Italian, or whatever it was, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the people, when we where there were from Hungarian, Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are lots of them, lots of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they-- they gave us some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] canes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You reverse the cane, and you put it in-- in their-- and you drag 'em out.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
